	" is a first-person shooter developed by id Software and published by Apogee Software in 1992. It follows the mission of a World War II Allied spy, William "B.J." Blazkowicz, to take down Hitler's Nazi regime. Also known as 
	[em 
		"Wolf3D
	]em
	", it is widely regarded as having helped popularize the first-person shooter genre on PC and is id's precursor to the wildly popular 
	[em 
		(__wikiLink|Movies-DOOM|Doom)
	]em
	" series.
	$LF
